cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.CL. 

The paper discusses deep learning and specifically focuses on sequence learning using generative RNNs. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper introduces a new dataset for predicting and classifying MNIST pen stroke sequences, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
